Mosley told Us Weekly that she was shocked when producers informed her of her character’s new arc.

item.description: Recommended Videos Hot on the heels of Coachella dropping its 2016 roster, The Governors Ball has now followed suit, unleashing a massive lineup for its sixth outing, which is set to take place at Randall’s Island Park on June 3-5. The big names here are obviously Kanye West, The Killers, M83 and Beck, but really, the whole lineup is quite strong, with representation from a number of genres of music, resulting in an eclectic and exciting group of artists.

item.title: Vincent Kartheiser And Alexis Bledel Filed For Divorce After 8 Years Of Marriage
item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: After eight years of marriage, Vincent Kartheiser and Alexis Bledel are divorcing. On August 10, Kartheiser, 43, filed for divorce from Bledel, 40, in New York’s Putnam County Court. Kartheiser’s agents have yet to comment on the matter, but PEOPLE verified through Bledel’s spokesperson. Us Weekly also verified the story. The cause for their breakup is unclear, and further information is anticipated. Alexis Bledel’s character exchanged scenes with Vincent Kartheiser In Mad MenIn Mad Men season 5, Alexis Bledel played insurance salesman Howard Dawes’ wife, Beth Dawes.
